!^m::
toWho := `from`
ccWho := `to`
subject := "`subject`"
body := "`body`"
Run outlook.exe
WinWait, Inbox
Sleep 1000
Send {Ctrl down}{Shift down}m{Ctrl up}{Shift up}
Send %toWho%{Esc}
Send {Tab}
Send %ccWho%{Esc}
Send {Tab}
Send %subject%
Send {Tab}
Send %body%
Sleep 1000
MsgBox,4,,Would You Like To Send This Email??
IfMsgBox Yes
                Send {Alt down}s{Alt up}
return
